 wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>sudo apt update\nsudo apt install gcc make openssl curl libbz2-dev libxml2-dev libjpeg-dev libpng-dev libfreetype6-dev libzip-dev libcurl4-openssl-dev</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>这里是ubuntu安装的依赖，如果是centos请将 apt-get替换成 yum</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>3. 编译前配置与编译安装</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>sudo useradd  -U  -M -s /sbin/nologin www</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>./configure --prefix=/usr/local/php --with-config-file-path=/usr/local/php/etc --enable-fpm --with-fpm-user=www --with-fpm-group=www --with-mysqli --with-pdo-mysql --with-iconv-dir --with-freetype-dir --with-jpeg-dir --with-png-dir --with-zlib --with-libxml-dir=/usr --enable-xml --disable-rpath --enable-bcmath --enable-shmop --enable-sysvsem --enable-inline-optimization --with-curl --enable-mbregex --enable-mbstring --enable-ftp --with-gd --with-openssl --with-mhash --enable-pcntl --enable-sockets --with-xmlrpc --enable-zip --enable-soap --without-pear --with-gettext --disable-fileinfo --enable-maintainer-zts\n\nmake -j2\n\nsudo make install</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>4. 安装后简单配置</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code># 复制源码包目录下面的php.ini-development开发版配置到php安装目录的ext目录下\ncp php.ini-development  /usr/local/php/etc/php.ini\n\n# 复制php安装目录的ext目录下的php-fpm.conf.default\ncp php-fpm.conf.default  php-fpm.conf\n\n# 复制php安装目录的ext/php-fpm.d目录下的www.conf.default\ncp www.conf.default www.conf\n\n# 编辑www.conf\nvim www.conf  # 找到user与group修改\n\nuser = www \ngroup = www</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>5. 创建快捷方式与启动测试</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>sudo ln -s /usr/local/php/b