s=\"wp-block-code\"><code># 进入php源码包扩展目录\ncd ~/src/php-7.3.6/ext/fileinfo</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":281} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/15649989231.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-281\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>2. 编译安装</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code># 使用phpize生成configure可执行文件\n/usr/local/php/bin/phpize\n\n# 执行编译，使用原php编译的配置\n./configure -with-php-config=/usr/local/php/bin/php-config\n\n# 安装\nmake -j2 &amp;&amp; sudo make install</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":282} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/DeepinScreenshot_select-area_20190805180126.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-282\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>3. 配置php.ini开启扩展</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>vim your_path/php.ini\n\n#　找到下面去掉注释\n;extension=fileinfo.so\n\n# 重启php-fpm</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->','PHP编译fileinfo扩展','','inherit','closed','closed','','280-revision-v1','','','2019-08-05 18:04:17','2019-08-05 10:04:17','',280,'http://long521.cn/2019/08/05/280-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(284,1,'2019-08-05 20:13:19','2019-08-05 12:13:19','<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>下载源码包</li><li>安装依赖</li><li>创建用户和组</li><li>编译安装mysql</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>1. 官网下载源码包</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code># wget mysql source code\nwget https://dev.mysql.com/get/Downloads/MySQL-5.7/mysql-boost-5.7.27.tar.gz\n\n# tar 解压\ntar -zxvf mysql-boost-5.7.27.tar.gz\n\n# cd 解压的mysql目录\ncd mysql-boost-5.7.27/\n\n#如下图</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":287} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/DeepinScreenshot_dde-desktop_20190806105442-1024x555.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-287\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":288} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/DeepinScreenshot_dde-desktop_20190806105556-1024x555.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-288\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":289} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/DeepinScreenshot_dde-desktop_20190806105631-1024x555.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-289\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>2. 安装依赖</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>＃ centos,fedora/redhat-OS\nsudo yum -y install cmake ncurses-devel libtirpc-devel\n\n# ubuntu,deepin,debian(debian-OS)\nsudo apt-get install cmake libncurses5 libncurses5-dev build-essential flex bison mpi-default-dev libicu-dev python-dev libbz2-dev -y</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>3.创建用户和组</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code># create group\ngroupadd mysql\n\n# create user\nuseradd -M -g mysql -s /sbin/false mysql</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>4. 开始编译安装ｍｙｓｑｌ</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code># 1. cmake配置\nsudo cmake \\\n-DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr/local/mysql \\\n-DMYSQL_DATADIR=/usr/local/mysql/data \\\n-DSYSCONFDIR=/etc \\\n-DWITH_MYISAM_STORAGE_ENGINE=1 \\\n-DWITH_INNOBASE_STORAGE_ENGINE=1 \\\n-DWITH_MEMORY_STORAGE_ENGINE=1 \\\n-DWITH_READLINE=1 \\\n-DMYSQL_UNIX_ADDR=/usr/local/mysql/logs/mysql.sock \\\n-DMYSQL_TCP_PORT=3306 \\\n-DENABLED_LOCAL_INFILE=1 \\\n-DWITH_PARTITION_STORAGE_ENGINE=1 \\\n-DEXTRA_CHARSETS=all \\\n-DDEFAULT_CHARSET=utf8 \\\n-DDEFAULT_COLLATION=utf8_general_ci \\\n-DENABLE_DOWNLOADS=1 -DWITH_BOOST=./boost\n\n# 2. 编译安装\nmake -j4 &amp;&amp; sudo make install</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>5. 安装成功后初始化配置</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code># 初始化\n/usr/local/mysql/bin/mysqld --initialize --user=mysql --basedir=/usr/local/mysql --datadir=/usr/local/mysql/data\n\n＃　上步可以看到初始化密码\n2019-08-05T05:46:46.601108Z 1 [Note] A temporary password is generated for root@localhost: D>1!lgqU/u5,\n\n＃　临时随机密码\nD>1!lgqU/u5,\n\n# 创建logs目录\nmkdir /usr/local/mysql/logs &amp;&amp; chown -R mysql:mysql logs/\n\n# 复制shell管理文件\ncp /usr/local/mysql/support-files/mysql.server /etc/init.d/mysqld\n\n# 添加到系统服务管理\nupdate-rc.d mysqld defaults\n\n# 启动mysqld\n/etc/init.d/mysqld start\n\n# 使用临时root密码登录mysql\n/usr/local/mysql/bin/mysql -uroot -p\n\n# 在mysql－shell里面修改密码\nset password=password(\"test123456\");\nflush privileges;</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Mysql编译安装','','publish','open','open','','mysql%e7%bc%96%e8%af%91%e5%ae%89%e8%a3%85','','','2019-08-22 15:18:49','2019-08-22 07:18:49','',0,'http://long521.cn/?p=284',0,'post','',0),(285,1,'2019-08-05 20:13:19','2019-08-05 12:13:19','<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>下载源码包</li><li>安装依赖</li><li>创建用户和组</li><li>编译安装mysql</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->','Mysql编译安装','','inherit','closed','closed','','284-revision-v1','','','2019-08-05 20:13:19','2019-08-05 12:13:19','',284,'http://long521.cn/2019/08/05/284-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(287,1,'2019-08-06 10:58:23','2019-08-06 02:58:23','','DeepinScreenshot_dde-desktop_20190806105442','','inherit','open','closed','','deepinscreenshot_dde-desktop_20190806105442','','','2019-08-06 10:58:23','2019-08-06 02:58:23','',284,'http://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/DeepinScreenshot_dde-desktop_20190806105442.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(288,1,'2019-08-06 10:58:30','2019-08-06 02:58:30','','DeepinScreenshot_dde-desktop_20190806105556','','inherit','open','closed','','deepinscreenshot_dde-desktop_2