->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>3. 创建软连接快速启动</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code># mv /usr/local/\ncd ..\nmv redis-5.0.5/ /usr/local/\n\n# create soft link to bin\nsudo ln -s /usr/local/redis-5.0.5/src/redis-server /usr/local/bin/\n\n# test start\nredis-server \n\n# test start and reload redis.conf\nredis-server /usr/local/redis-5.0.5/redis.conf</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->','redis源码安装(linux)','','inherit','closed','closed','','304-revision-v1','','','2019-08-09 11:18:28','2019-08-09 03:18:28','',304,'http://long521.cn/2019/08/09/304-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(308,1,'2019-08-09 14:09:28','2019-08-09 06:09:28','<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>下载php源代码并解压</li><li>安装依赖</li><li>编译安装</li><li>安装成功配置</li><li>启动与测试</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>1. 下载php7.3源代码</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>wget http://download.long521.cn/php-7.3.6.tar.gz\n\ntar -zxvf  php-7.3.6.tar.gz\n\ncd  php-7.3.6</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>2.  安装依赖</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code># install dependent for ubuntu,deepin（debian）\nsudo apt update\nsudo apt install gcc gcc-c++ make openssl-devel curl-devel libjpeg-devel libpng-devel libfreetype6-devel libzip-devel libcurl4-openssl-devel\n\n----------------------------------------------------------------------\n# install dependent for centos,fedora (redhat)\nsudo yum -y install gcc gcc-c++ make openssl-devel curl-devel libxml2-devel libjpeg-devel libpng-devel libfreetype6-devel libzip-devel libcurl4-openssl-devel freetype-devel</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>这里是ubuntu安装的依赖，如果是centos请将 apt-get替换成 yum</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>3. 编译前配置与编译安装</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>sudo useradd  -U  -M -s /sbin/nologin www</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>./configure --prefix=/usr/local/php --with-config-file-path=/usr/local/php/etc --enable-fpm --with-fpm-user=www --with-fpm-group=www --with-mysqli --with-pdo-mysql --with-iconv-dir --with-freetype-dir --with-jpeg-dir --with-png-dir --with-zlib --with-libxml-dir=/usr --enable-xml --disable-rpath --enable-bcmath --enable-shmop --enable-sysvsem --enable-inline-optimization --with-curl --enable-mbregex --enable-mbstring --enable-ftp --with-gd --with-openssl --with-mhash --enable-pcntl --enable-sockets --with-xmlrpc --enable-zip --enable-soap --without-pear --with-gettext --enable-fileinfo --enable-maintainer-zts\n\nmake -j2\n\nsudo make install</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>4. 安装后简单配置</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code># 复制源码包目录下面的php.ini-development开发版配置到php安装目录的ext目录下\ncp php.ini-development  /usr/local/php/etc/php.ini\n\n# 复制php安装目录的ext目录下的php-fpm.conf.default\ncp php-fpm.conf.default  php-fpm.conf\n\n# 复制php安装目录的ext/php-fpm.d目录下的www.conf.default\ncp www.conf.default www.conf\n\n# 编辑www.conf\nvim www.conf  # 找到user与group修改\n\nuser = www \ngroup = www</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>5. 创建快捷方式与启动测试</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>sudo ln -s /usr/local/php/bin/php  /usr/local/bin\nphp -v # 查看php版本信息\n\nsudo ln -s /usr/local/php/sbin/php-fpm  /usr/local/bin\nphp-fpm    # 启动php-fpm\nps -ef | grep php-fpm  # 查看进程</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>到了这里php就是编译安装好了，如果需要通过浏览器访问，可以看本站的另一篇文章 “编译安装nginx”，nginx配置了php-fpm支持</p><p>sudo vi /usr/local/nginx/html/index.php  # 编写测试代码</p><p>&lt;?php</p><p>  phpinfo();</p><p>?&gt;</p><p>浏览器访问  127.0.0.1/index.php  测试</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->','编译安装PHP7.3','','inherit','closed','closed','','210-revision-v1','','','2019-08-09 14:09:28','2019-08-09 06:09:28','',210,'http://long521.cn/2019/08/09/210-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(309,1,'2019-08-09 14:15:08','2019-08-09 06:15:08','<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>官网下载源码包，解压</li><li>安装依赖</li><li>编译安装</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>1.下载源码并解压</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>wget http://download.long521.cn/nginx-1.16.0.tar.gz\n\ntar -zxvf nginx-1.16.0.tar.gz\n\ncd nginx-1.16.0</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>2. 安装依赖与工具</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code># install dependent for ubuntu\nsudo apt-get install make gcc gcc-c++ libpcre3-devel libssl-devel libxml2-dev   libperl-devel libtool-devel openssl-devel pcre-devel\n\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# install dependent for centos,fedora (radhat)\nsudo yum -y install make gcc gcc-c++ libpcre3-devel libssl-devel libxml2-dev   libperl-devel libtool-devel openssl-devel pcre-devel</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>3. 编译前配置与安装</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>sudo useradd  -U  -M -s /sbin/nologin www</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>./configure --prefix=/usr/local/nginx --with-http_ssl_module --with-stream --with-mail=dynamic  --user=www  --group=user --sbin-path=/usr/local/bin --with-pcre\n\nmake -j2\n\nsudo make install</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>4. 安装成功后简单配置与启动</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>vim /usr/local/nginx/conf/nginx.conf  //将下面代码全部覆盖进去重写</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>user  www www;\n	worker_processes  2;\n\n	#error_log  logs/error.log;\n	#error_log  logs/error.log  notice;\n	#error_log  logs/error.log  info;\n\n	#pid        logs/nginx.pid;\n\n\n	events {\n	    worker_connections  1024;\n	}\n\n\n	http {\n	    include       mime.types;\n	    default_type  application/octet-stream;\n\n	    #log_format  main  \'$remote_addr - $remote_user [$time_local] \"$request\" \'\n	    #                  \'$status $body_bytes_sent \"$http_referer\" \'\n	    #                  \'\"$http_user_agent\" \"$http_x_forwarded_for\"\';\n\n	    #access_log  logs/access.log  main;\n\n	    sendfile        on;\n	    #tcp_nopush     on;\n\n	    #keepalive_timeout  0;\n	    keepalive_timeout  65;\n\n	    #gzip  on;\n\n	    server {\n	        listen       80;\n	        server_name  localhost;\n\n	        #charset koi8-r;\n\n	        #access_log  logs/host.access.log  main;\n\n	        location / {\n	            root   html;\n	            index  index.html index.htm;\n	        }\n\n	        #error_page  404              /404.html;\n\n	        # redirect server error pages to the static page /50x.html\n	        #\n	        error_page   500 502 503 504  /50x.html;\n	        location = /50x.html {\n	            root   html;\n	        }\n\n	        # proxy the PHP scripts to Apache listening on 127.0.0.1:80\n	        #\n	        #location ~ \\.php$ {\n	        #    proxy_pass   http://127.0.0.1;\n	        #}\n\n	        # pass the PHP scripts to FastCGI server listening on 127.0.0.1:9000\n	        #\n	        location ~ \\.php$ {\n	            root           html;\n	            fastcgi_pass   127.0.0.1:9000;\n	            fastcgi_index  index.php;\n	            fastcgi_param  SCRIPT_FILENAME  $document_root$fastcgi_script_name;\n	            include        fastcgi_params;\n	        }\n\n	        # deny access to .htaccess files, if Apache\'s document root\n	        # concurs with nginx\'s one\n	        #\n	        location ~ /\\.ht {\n	            deny  all;\n	        }\n	    }\n\n\n	    # another virtual host using mix of IP-, name-, and port-based configuration\n	    #\n	    #server {\n	    #    listen       8000;\n	    #    listen       somename:8080;\n	    #    server_name  somename  alias  another.alias;\n\n	    #    location / {\n	    #        root   html;\n	    #        index  index.html index.htm;\n	    #    }\n	    #}\n\n\n	    # HTTPS server\n	    #\n	    #server {\n	    #    listen       443 ssl;\n	    #    server_name  localhost;\n\n	    #    ssl_certificate      cert.pem;\n	    #    ssl_certificate_key  cert.key;\n\n	    #    ssl_session_cache    shared:SSL:1m;\n	    #    ssl_session_timeout  5m;\n\n	    #    ssl_ciphers  HIGH:!aNULL:!MD5;\n	    #    ssl_prefer_server_ciphers  on;\n\n	    #    location / {\n	    #        root   html;\n	    #        index  index.html index.htm;\n	    #    }\n	    #}\n\n	}</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>以上的配置中开启了php的支持配置，如果需要支持php的话需要安装php并启动php-fpm，可以看本站的编译安装php7.3</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>5. 启动nginx并测试</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>sudo nginx   # 启动nginx\n\nps -ef | grep nginx  # 查看nginx进程\n\ncurl 127.0.0.1  或  浏览器访问 测试是否成功</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->','编译安装nginx','','inherit','closed','closed','','207-revision-v1','','','2019-08-09 14:15:08','2019-08-09 06:15:08','',207,'http://long521.cn/2019/08/09/207-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(310,1,'2019-08-12 14:36:44','2019-08-12 06:36:44','<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>ubuntu/Linux 卸载原flame</li><li>git clone Flame源码</li><li>安装依赖及编译工具</li><li>编译安装flame</li><li>配置快捷键</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>1. 卸载原有的flame</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>sudo apt remove flame</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>2. 下载flame源码</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code 