 href=\"https://xdebug.org/files/xdebug-2.7.2.tgz\">https://xdebug.org/files/xdebug-2.7.2.tgz</a><br><br>2.  解压缩<br>tar -zxf xdebug-2.7.2.tar<br><br>3.  进入解压缩后的xdebug-2.7.2目录下<br>cd    xdebug-2.7.2.tar <br><br>4. 使用phpize生成对应的configure文件<br>/usr/local/php7.2/bin/phpize<br><br>5.  配置xdebug预安装<br>./configure --with-php-config=/usr/local/php7.2/bin/php-config<br><br>6. 开始编译安装<br>make -j  &amp;&amp; make install      # -j选项有提高编译速度<br><br>编译安装成功如图：<br><br></pre>\n<!-- /wp:verse -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":189} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/U@8OTH_EUY0TFUR8.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-189\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>编辑php.ini开启xdebug扩展并配置一些选项</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:verse -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-verse\">1.&nbsp; &nbsp;找到你的php加载的php.ini<br>脚本运行phpinfo();查看加载的php.ini位置<br><br>2.&nbsp; &nbsp;vim&nbsp; /your-php-ini<br>----------------------------------------------------------------------<br>[Xdebug]<br>zend_extension = xdebug.so<strong><br></strong>xdebug.auto_trace = 0<br>xdebug.remote_autostart=On<br>xdebug.trace_output_dir = /tmp/xdebug<strong><br></strong>xdebug.profiler_enable = 1<br>xdebug.profiler_output_dir = /tmp/xdebug/profiler<strong><br></strong>xdebug.max_nesting_level = 100<br>xdebug.remote_enable = 1<br>xdebug.remote_host = 192.168.1.116&nbsp; &nbsp;# 这里写你的本机内网ip<br>xdebug.remote_port = 9427&nbsp; &nbsp; #&nbsp; 端口号后面要用<br>xdebug.remote_handler = dbgp<br>xdebug.idekey = PHPSTORM <br>------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br><br>3. 停止php-fpm 再启动<br>&nbsp;kill -INT `cat&nbsp; /usr/local/php7.2/var/run/php-fpm.pid`<br>或者<br>&nbsp;pkill php-fpm <br>或者<br>service php-fpm restart<br> <br></pre>\n<!-- /wp:verse -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>配置PHPStorm支持xdebug</strong></li><li></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":191} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/KL85@FGXRSIYLOHC3-1024x600-1024x600.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-191\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":192} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/NX@HB6REJ_E3T3ZTOH-1024x716.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-192\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>好了接下来可以测试了</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":194} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/YE6JSNXJF9P4PZP1CWF8W4-1024x494.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-194\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->','Linux配置PhpStorm Xdebug','','inherit','closed','closed','','188-revision-v1','','','2019-08-22 19:10:24','2019-08-22 11:10:24','',188,'http://long521.cn/2019/08/22/188-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(398,1,'2019-08-22 21:32:26','2019-08-22 13:32:26','<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>下载php源代码并解压</li><li>安装依赖</li><li>编译安装</li><li>安装成功配置</li><li>启动与测试</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>1. 下载php7.3源代码</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>wget http://download.long521.cn/php-7.3.6.tar.gz\n\ntar -zxvf  php-7.3.6.tar.gz\n\ncd  php-7.3.6</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>2.  安装依赖</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code># install dependent for ubuntu,deepin（debian）\nsudo apt update\nsudo apt install gcc gcc-c++ make openssl-dev libjpeg-dev libpng-dev libfreetype6-dev libzip-dev libcurl4-openssl-dev\n\n----------------------------------------------------------------------\n# install dependent for centos,fedora (redhat)\nsudo yum -y install gcc gcc-c++ make openssl-devel curl-devel libxml2-devel libjpeg-devel libpng-devel libzip-devel freetype-devel</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>这里是ubuntu安装的依赖，如果是centos请将 apt-get替换成 yum</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>3. 编译前配置与编译安装</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>sudo useradd  -U  -M -s /sbin/nologin www</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>./configure --prefix=/usr/local/php --with-config-file-path=/usr/local/php/etc --enable-fpm --with-fpm-user=www --with-fpm-group=www --with-mysqli --with-pdo-mysql --with-iconv-dir --with-freetype-dir --with-jpeg-dir --with-png-dir --with-zlib --with-libxml-dir=/usr --enable-xml --disable-rpath --enable-bcmath --enable-shmop --enable-sysvsem --enable-inline-optimization --with-curl --enable-mbregex --enable-mbstring --enable-ftp --with-gd --with-openssl --with-mhash --enable-pcntl --enable-sockets --with-xmlrpc --enable-zip --enable-soap --without-pear --with-gettext --enable-fileinfo --enable-maintainer-zts\n\nmake -j2\n\nsudo make install</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>4. 安装后简单配置</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code># 复制源码包目录下面的php.ini-development开发版配置到php安装目录的ext目录下\ncp php.ini-development  /usr/local/php/etc/php.ini\n\n# 复制php安装目录的ext目录下的php-fpm.conf.default\ncp php-fpm.conf.default  php-fpm.conf\n\n# 复制php安装目录的ext/php-fpm.d目录下的www.conf.default\ncp www.conf.default www.conf\n\n# 编辑www.conf\nvim www.conf  # 找到user与group修改\n\nuser = www \ngroup = www</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>5. 创建快捷方式与启动测试</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>sudo ln -s /usr/local/php/bin/php  /usr/local/bin\nphp -v # 查看php版本信息\n\nsudo ln -s /usr/local/php/sbin/php-fpm  /usr/local/bin\nphp-fpm    # 启动php-fpm\nps -ef | grep php-fpm  # 查看进程</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>到了这里php就是编译安装好了，如果需要通过浏览器访问，可以看本站的另一篇文章 “编译安装nginx”，nginx配置了php-fpm支持</p><p>sudo vi /usr/local/nginx/html/index.php  # 编写测试代码</p><p>&lt;?php</p><p>  phpinfo();</p><p>?&gt;</p><p>浏览器访问  127.0.0.1/index.php  测试</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->','编译安装PHP7.3','','inherit','closed','closed','','210-revision-v1','','','2019-08-22 21:32:26','2019-08-22 13:32:26','',210,'http://long521.cn/2019/08/22/210-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(400,1,'2019-08-23 14:45:00','2019-08-23 06:45:00','','hua','','inherit','open','closed','','hua','','','2019-08-23 14:45:00','2019-08-23 06:45:00','',0,'http://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/hua.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(401,1,'2019-08-23 14:45:01','2019-08-23 06:45:01','','jiu','','inherit','open','closed','','jiu','','','2019-08-23 14:45:01','2019-08-23 06:45:01','',0,'http://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/jiu.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(402,1,'2019-08-23 14:45:01','2019-08-23 06:45:01','','niu','','inherit','open','closed','','niu','','','2019-08-23 14:45:01','2019-08-23 06:45:01','',0,'http://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/niu.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(403,1,'2019-08-23 14:45:01','2019-08-23 06:45:01','','huo','','inherit','open','closed','','huo','','','2019-08-23 14:45:01','2019-08-23 06:45:01','',0,'http://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/huo.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(404,1,'2019-08-23 14:45:02','2019-08-23 06:45:02','','qq','','inherit','open','closed','','qq','','','2019-08-23 14:45:02','2019-08-23 06:45:02','',0,'http://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/qq.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(405,1,'2019-08-23 14:45:02','2019-08-23 06:45:02','','hu','','inherit','open','closed','','hu','','','2019-08-23 14:45:02','2019-08-23 06:45:02','',0,'http://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/hu.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(406,1,'2019-08-23 14:45:02','2019-08-23 06:45:02','','dun','','inherit','open','closed','','dun','','','2019-08-23 14:45:02','2019-08-23 06:45:02','',0,'http://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/dun.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(407,1,'2019-08-23 14:45:03','2019-08-23 06:45:03','','long','','inherit','open','closed','','long-2','','','2019-08-23 14:45:03','2019-08-23 06:45:03','',0,'http://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/long.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(409,1,'2019-08-24 12:57:28','2019-08-24 04:57:28','<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>下载通用二进制压缩包</li><li>创建mysql用户和组</li><li>执行命令授权并注册</li><li>修改默认密码</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>本文以安装mysql8.0和mysql5.7为例</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>1. 官网下载通用二进制压缩包</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>mysql5.7</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code># 进入下载目录，下载的文件都放在此目录，可改变\ncd ~/Downloads\n\n# 下载官网链接 （不保证连接一直有效）\nwget https://dev.mysql.com/get/Downloads/MySQL-5.7/mysql-5.7.27-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64.tar.gz\n\n# 解压\ntar -zxvf mysql-5.7.27-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64.tar.gz</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>mysql8.0</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code># 进入下载目录，下载的文件都放在此目录，可改变\ncd ~/Downloads\n\n# 下载官网链接 （不保证连接一直有效）\nwget https://dev.mysql.com/get/Downloads/MySQL-8.0/mysql-8.0.17-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64.tar.xz\n\n# 解压tar.xz文件：先 xz -d xxx.tar.xz 将 xxx.tar.xz解压成 xxx.tar 然后，再用 tar xvf xxx.tar来解包。\nxz -d mysql-8.0.17-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64.tar.xz\ntar xvf mysql-8.0.17-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64.tar\n</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>2. 创建mysql用户和组,安装依赖</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>创建用户和组(注意使用sudo权限)</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code># create user&amp;group\ngroupadd mysql\nuseradd -r -g mysql -s /bin/false mysql\n\n# move mysql\nmv ~/Downloads/mysql-8.0 /usr/local/mysql\n\n# cd mysql dir\ncd /usr/local/mysql\n\n# install dependents\n# redhat系列使用yum安装\nyum install libaio ncurses-compat-libs\n\n# debian系列使用apt安装\napt-get install libaio1</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>3. 执行命令授权并注册</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>注册安装(使用sudo权限)</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code># 进入上部移动的mysql目录\ncd /usr/local/mysql\n\n# 初始化\nbin/mysqld --initialize --user=mysql\n#这里初始化成功会看到临时的密码需要记下来等会登陆要用\n\n# 安全设置&amp;安全启动\nbin/mysql_ssl_rsa_setup\nbin/mysqld_safe --user=mysql &amp;\n\n# 加入系统管理\ncp support-files/mysql.server /etc/init.d/mysql.server</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>查看Mysql是否启动</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>ps -ef | grep mysql\n\n/etc/init.d/mysql.service status</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>4。 登陆myslq并修改临时密码</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>/usr/local/mysql/bin/mysql -uroot -p\n# 这里回车输入上面初始化时记录的临时密码\n\n# 登陆成功后修改密码\n# mysql5.7\nset password=password(\'test1234\');\n\n# mysql8.0\nalter user root@localhost identified by \'test1234\';\n\n# 刷新权限，立即生效\nflush privileges;</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-0 is-cropped\"></ul>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->','通用二进制安装Mysql','','trash','open','open','','%e9%80%9a%e7%94%a8%e4%ba%8c%e8%bf%9b%e5%88%b6%e5%ae%89%e8%a3%85mysql__trashed','','','2019-08-24 14:39:13','2019-08-24 06:39:13','',0,'http://long521.cn/?p=409',0,'post','',0),(410,1,'2019-08-24 12:57:28','2019-08-24 04:57:28','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2019-08-24 -&nbsp;<a href=\"http://wp.lo/category/php/\">PHP</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>下载通用二进制压缩包</li><li>创建mysql用户和组</li><li>执行命令授权并注册</li><li>修改默认密码</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>本文以安装mysql8.0和mysql5.7为例</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>1. 官网下载通用二进制压缩包</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- w